This package includes a modified install script for xfitter with HATHOR 
and a selection of common PDF sets.

USAGE:

Make sure the script is executable on your machine and run it:
    chmod +x install-xfitter
    ./install-xfitter 2.0.1

To run a fixed-PDF study (LHAPDF analysis), you can do for example:
    source setup.sh
    cd run/LHAPDF_analysis_run
    xfitter
    xfitter-draw --bands --q2all output
Also check out xfitter-draw --help to see what other plot options you have.
